data.description: Located in the Upstate's fastest growing area, this better-than-new 4BR, 3.5BA home has been well-maintained and is ready to go.  Step in to find a 2-story foyer with 5-inch hand scraped hardwood floors and archways into  formal living room on your right which leads into dining room with coffered ceiling.  The huge great room also has coffered ceiling, gas logs and is open to the breakfast area and kitchen with tons of counter and cabinet space.  The kitchen boasts of stainless double ovens, gas cooktop, dishwasher, microwave, breakfast bar and center island.  Head upstairs to the enormous master BR with vaulted ceilings and large MBA with separate tub and tile shower, double sink vanity, linen closet and large walk-in closet.  Other BRs are spacious with one having an ensuite bath and the other 2 having a Jack-and-Jill between. Architectural shingles, tankless water heater, fenced yard, sprinklers front and back, oversized 2-car garage and corner lot make this home the total package.  Come get it before it's gone!
